      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same device class and operating regime as the COU. Five operating points span the clinical VAD operating envelope. Confidence ~55%; the validation pump is a generic geometry rather than the specific commercial impeller, introducing geometric extrapolation uncertainty. This gap is explicitly documented and bounded by geometric similarity analysis (impeller specific speed within 8% of COU device)."
    },
