      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms; all simulations converged to L2 residual <1e-6 for velocity and pressure, <1e-5 for hemolysis scalar. Round-off error assessed as negligible (double precision). Confidence ~65%; residual convergence criterion for hemolysis scalar was relaxed from 1e-6 to 1e-5 at two operating points due to oscillatory convergence behaviour, explicitly documented. Level 2 achieved meets level 2 required."
