      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by independent analyst. Boundary condition application, material property assignments, and hemolysis model parameter inputs verified against documented simulation plan. Confidence ~60%; independent review was performed by a single reviewer rather than a formal review board, and this is explicitly noted as a process limitation. No discrepancies found in the independent review."
    },
    {
