      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) selected based on literature review of available hemolysis constitutive models. SST k-omega turbulence model used for flow. Confidence in model form ~50%; the power-law hemolysis model has known limitations under complex multi-axial shear paths characteristic of centrifugal pumps, and this is explicitly documented. Sensitivity analysis comparing Giersiepen-Wurzinger to the Arora model shows <15% NIH difference, providing partial corroboration. Level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
